<div id=3D"outline-container-orgc57b582" class=3D"outline-3">
<h3 id=3D"orgc57b582">Martin Jambon announced</h3>
<div class=3D"outline-text-3" id=3D"text-orgc57b582">
<p>
ATD 4.0.0 adds experimental support for imports between ATD files.
</p>

<p>
This allows splitting schemas across multiple files in a natural way.
</p>

<p>
Currently supported in:
</p>
